column1: Baby Barnaby's////I came here because of their reviews but regret it sooo much! There is a long wait line in a very traditional way that you have to write your name and stay in the hot sunny patio to be seated maybe in an hour after!! They definitely need a better system to do this. Either take the customers number and call them when the table is ready so they can at least sit in their cara with the AC or have an online waiting in Yelp. Food was good but nothing extraordinary that worth the wait.
